            "type": "canvas",
            "canvasData": "{}",
            "teacherNotes": "### Two Ways to Say \"Read!\"\n\n- **Читай!** (imperfective) - Read! / Keep reading! / Start reading!\n- **Прочитай!** (perfective) - Read it! / Finish reading it!\n\nBoth are commands to read, but they give different instructions."
          }
        ]
      }
